snippet.title: Mission Craft - Arcade - Star Craft - Galloping Ghost Arcade - Sun - 2000
snippet.description: Here is a play through of the first 3 levels of MISSION CRAFT!  Released from Sun in 2000.   Come play it at the Galloping Ghost Arcade in Brookfield, IL...the only arcade in the US to have this arcade game (as of 09/03/2012).  Currently the world record is held here at the Galloping Ghost Arcade by Matt Rocco!
